<h3>This is OUBusSH!</h3>
<p>OUBusSH aka Oulu University Bus Stop Helper is designed to be an easy-to-use lightweight alternative to browsing Google Maps or Oulunjoukkoliikenne website in order to find out which bus takes you to where you want to go. All you need to do is to select one of the target destinations that are on the main page and it'll show you a list busses going that way from the bus stops near the Oulu University.
